" alt+e+[: 前一条报错
noremap ᜢᜠ <ESC>:cp<CR>
inoremap ᜢᜠ <ESC>:cp<CR>
" alt+e+alt+<cr>:  显示详细错误信息
noremap ᜢᜣ <ESC>:cc<CR>
inoremap ᜢᜣ <ESC>:cc<CR>

